  "label": "Graveward Ridge",
  "description": "Graveward Ridge rises as a long, broken massif above Cyrenth Vale’s ash plains, its slopes cut by rift-scarred gullies and shelves of vitrified fallout. The summit line carries old fortification terraces and shuttered revetments, their angular stonework blackened by centuries of particulate storms. Bruise-hued aurorae stain the snowless heights, casting a cold, veiled light over rock faces polished by abrasive winds. Scree fields and collapsed switchbacks mark the principal approaches, enforcing the ridge’s character as a natural bastion within a siege world.",
